{{# markdown }}
## {{ title }}

<span class="label evo-label" data-evo-background-color="success-color">Version: {{ package.organisms.conversational_form.version }}</span>
{{#is conversational-form.product_suite_bp 'true' }}<span class="label evo-label" data-evo-background-color="sapphire-bright">Benefits Portals</span>{{/is}}
{{#is conversational-form.product_suite_comm 'true' }}<span class="label evo-label" data-evo-background-color="amethyst-bright">Communication Sites</span>{{/is}}

Conversational forms are used as a non-traditional way of collecting data from a user. These forms build dynamically based on the answer from the previous question. Conversational Forms can build on each previous question by continuing to display the previous answers to the user as more questions get asked.
{{/ markdown }}

